1
00:00:07,400 --> 00:00:11,460
♪Just To Meet You, you fell for me♪

2
00:00:11,480 --> 00:00:15,460
♪Just to meet me, into my trap you fell♪

3
00:00:15,460 --> 00:00:19,240
♪Wanna try a breathless love?♪

4
00:00:19,240 --> 00:00:23,490
♪Every move hits the heart, close and sure♪

5
00:00:23,490 --> 00:00:27,460
♪Just To Meet You, you love my playful charm♪

6
00:00:27,460 --> 00:00:31,480
♪Just to meet me,
my romantic little schemes for you♪

7
00:00:31,480 --> 00:00:35,170
♪Wanna play another brand-new game?♪

8
00:00:35,170 --> 00:00:40,360
♪Layer by layer, we close the gap♪

9
00:00:40,380 --> 00:00:47,140
=Just To Meet You=

10
00:00:47,300 --> 00:00:50,340
(Ten years ago)

11
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:54,070
(Jiang Xiaodi, Jiang Niannian's Brother)
I can skip meals,

12
00:00:54,520 --> 00:00:55,710
but Xiaodi's still little,

13
00:00:56,520 --> 00:00:57,880
at least let him eat something.

14
00:00:58,320 --> 00:00:59,200
Eat?

15
00:01:00,110 --> 00:01:01,320
Where would we get the money

16
00:01:01,320 --> 00:01:03,150
to feed two useless mouths?

17
00:01:03,840 --> 00:01:04,840
If you ask me,

18
00:01:05,070 --> 00:01:06,400
you two shouldn't even go to school.

19
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:09,040
Talk to them properly.

20
00:01:09,310 --> 00:01:11,760
Niannian is sensible.

21
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:13,070
As for school,

22
00:01:13,920 --> 00:01:14,950
you're not going anymore.

23
00:01:17,310 --> 00:01:18,590
Why can't I go to school?

24
00:01:18,920 --> 00:01:21,590
Because Qingqing
needs to live well in France.

25
00:01:21,840 --> 00:01:23,020
She needs brushes and paint.

26
00:01:23,020 --> 00:01:23,950
And she has tuition to pay.

27
00:01:25,130 --> 00:01:26,350
Did you wire Qingqing the money?

28
00:01:26,710 --> 00:01:27,550
Yeah, it's sent.

29
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:42,510
Our Qingqing

30
00:01:42,510 --> 00:01:45,120
(Jiang Qingqing Amount)
will be a great artist.

31
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:48,150
Your family got such a good kid.

32
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:50,280
That's your ancestors' blessing.

33
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:00,920
(If I had money,)

34
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:02,430
(I could take Xiaodi away.)

35
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:04,430
(Why don't I have money!)

36
00:02:05,350 --> 00:02:06,540
90 million, going once.

37
00:02:06,540 --> 00:02:07,790
=Episode 6=
=Tears of a Fool in Love=

38
00:02:07,790 --> 00:02:09,910
(Jiang Qingqing, Jiang Niannian's Stepsister)
90 million, twice.

39
00:02:09,910 --> 00:02:11,090
100 million.

40
00:02:11,910 --> 00:02:13,240
100 million!

41
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:15,870
The top bid has hit 100 million.

42
00:02:15,870 --> 00:02:17,150
Any higher?

43
00:02:17,750 --> 00:02:18,680
I didn't expect

44
00:02:18,750 --> 00:02:21,870
you'd bring me to such an elite auction.

45
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:26,630
Because you're a top student
from Saint Martins in France,

46
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:29,120
and also my mother's alumna.

47
00:02:29,910 --> 00:02:31,430
You're worthy of being my companion.

48
00:02:32,710 --> 00:02:33,910
You're so good to me.

49
00:02:37,310 --> 00:02:38,800
100 million. Sold!

50
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:40,280
Congrats to that gentleman.

51
00:02:42,390 --> 00:02:43,240
Next,

52
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:45,520
let's welcome the host and his companion

53
00:02:45,710 --> 00:02:48,080
to present the crown

54
00:02:48,080 --> 00:02:49,870
to tonight's most valuable "item."

55
00:02:51,470 --> 00:02:52,870
(I shouldn't have brought her)

56
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:54,310
(to this filthy place.)

57
00:02:55,310 --> 00:02:58,470
(But I couldn't resist
watching her suffer for me.)

58
00:03:20,630 --> 00:03:21,520
(Ye Lang.)

59
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:23,360
(You brought Jiang Qingqing here on purpose.)

60
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:24,560
(Was it all to shame me?)

61
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:26,590
(Why does punishing her)

62
00:03:26,590 --> 00:03:27,960
(make me feel bad?)

63
00:03:28,910 --> 00:03:30,840
(I want everyone to see clearly)

64
00:03:31,190 --> 00:03:34,280
(the woman by Ye Lang's side
will only be me.)

65
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:40,080
Sir.

66
00:03:41,150 --> 00:03:43,400
You can enjoy your auction item now.

67
00:04:04,990 --> 00:04:06,280
No rush.

68
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:07,870
The night's still long.

69
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:09,750
Let's take our time.

70
00:04:12,590 --> 00:04:14,030
The bed's too soft.

71
00:04:15,030 --> 00:04:16,270
Look at this table.

72
00:04:16,270 --> 00:04:17,430
Isn't that more exciting?

73
00:04:19,270 --> 00:04:20,430
Go wait over there.

74
00:04:35,190 --> 00:04:37,190
The hosts sent something over.

75
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,800
Want to come take a look?

76
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:54,000
You just said I could enjoy myself.

77
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:58,920
Why act all proper now?

78
00:05:10,310 --> 00:05:11,160
Put me down.

79
00:05:11,750 --> 00:05:12,600
Put me down!

80
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:19,600
Young Master,

81
00:05:20,190 --> 00:05:21,430
you tricked me into coming here.

82
00:05:21,830 --> 00:05:23,360
Wasn't it just to test my feelings?

83
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:28,390
Where did he kiss you just now?

84
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:34,960
You guess.

85
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:40,720
♪Bit by bit, marking you with kisses♪

86
00:05:41,210 --> 00:05:44,900
♪Like shadows entwined in the night♪

87
00:05:45,310 --> 00:05:46,800
♪You are mine♪

88
00:05:46,950 --> 00:05:47,790
Ye Lang!

89
00:05:48,270 --> 00:05:49,430
I'm your companion tonight!

90
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:55,830
Let me out!

91
00:05:57,900 --> 00:06:01,810
♪I love you, with no limits♪

92
00:06:02,030 --> 00:06:03,890
♪Crimson bite marks♪

93
00:06:04,080 --> 00:06:07,630
♪Like I need you, and can't stop♪

94
00:06:10,070 --> 00:06:11,390
If I hadn't come,

95
00:06:12,310 --> 00:06:13,360
would you have...

96
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:15,180
♪The night melts♪

97
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:17,120
I belong only to you.

98
00:06:18,560 --> 00:06:19,880
♪A tender dream♪

99
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:21,750
You belong only to me.

100
00:06:28,180 --> 00:06:31,880
♪There's clearly no breeze in here♪

101
00:06:32,290 --> 00:06:34,450
♪Why is the fire slipping out of control♪

102
00:06:34,450 --> 00:06:36,280
♪The heat is rising♪

103
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:40,880
Jiang Niannian!

104
00:06:41,190 --> 00:06:42,040
Ye Lang is mine!

105
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:43,920
Hands off him!

106
00:06:44,080 --> 00:06:44,950
Hands off him!

107
00:06:44,950 --> 00:06:45,870
(Jiang Qingqing.)

108
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:47,510
(A man I don't want)

109
00:06:47,870 --> 00:06:48,870
(isn't yours either.)

110
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:06,430
(Since the Li family
has no clue about Xiaodi,)

111
00:07:07,070 --> 00:07:08,480
(I shouldn't stay in this den of danger.)

112
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:09,320
(I'd better leave now.)

113
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:11,400
(Ye Lang.)

114
00:07:11,610 --> 00:07:12,480
(This time)

115
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:13,560
(I truly have to say goodbye.)

116
00:07:35,780 --> 00:07:38,700
(Kill Ye Lang, Jiang Xiaodi will be back.)

117
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:44,960
Mr. Zhong,

118
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:49,040
let me handle it.

119
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:51,000
Ms. Jiang,

120
00:07:51,390 --> 00:07:52,390
why are you still here?

121
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:54,160
From what I know of Young Master,

122
00:07:54,750 --> 00:07:56,510
trying to please him like this won't work.

123
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:59,040
As long as

124
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:00,360
he hasn't driven me away,

125
00:08:00,830 --> 00:08:02,720
I'm still his wife.

126
00:08:06,430 --> 00:08:07,560
Good luck then.

127
00:09:02,670 --> 00:09:04,270
You shameless girl,

128
00:09:04,270 --> 00:09:05,270
you still dare show up?

129
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:08,360
Watch your mouth.

130
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:10,720
You're nothing more than a plaything.

131
00:09:12,270 --> 00:09:13,390
Let me remind you,

132
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:14,600
the Li family

133
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:16,390
sent an invitation to the Jiang family.

134
00:09:17,390 --> 00:09:18,510
Besides,

135
00:09:18,510 --> 00:09:19,910
that day's auction

136
00:09:20,200 --> 00:09:22,440
was just a little game between us.

137
00:09:22,720 --> 00:09:24,080
You got locked in the restroom.

138
00:09:24,790 --> 00:09:25,750
Isn't that clear enough?

139
00:09:25,750 --> 00:09:26,630
So what?

140
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:28,600
My background is spotless.

141
00:09:29,120 --> 00:09:30,790
I'm more fit for the Li family than you.

142
00:09:32,030 --> 00:09:33,150
But now,

143
00:09:33,630 --> 00:09:35,390
I'm the one who married Ye Lang.

144
00:09:35,750 --> 00:09:36,590
You...

145
00:09:44,910 --> 00:09:45,840
Honey,

146
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:48,080
you're here.

147
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:51,200
You sent the people

148
00:09:51,240 --> 00:09:52,600
who raised you to prison,

149
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:54,390
you don't deserve to be his wife!

150
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:56,600
I'm the one who sent them to jail.

151
00:09:59,080 --> 00:09:59,920
Ms. Jiang.

152
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:02,000
The driver is ready.

153
00:10:02,390 --> 00:10:03,390
Please leave.

154
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:10,720
The outsider's gone.

155
00:10:11,570 --> 00:10:12,500
Young Master.

156
00:10:14,790 --> 00:10:15,630
Time for your medicine.

157
00:10:52,670 --> 00:10:53,510
(Jiang Niannian.)

158
00:10:54,240 --> 00:10:56,390
(So you really are giving up on me?)

159
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:03,270
Your carotid pulse frequency

160
00:11:03,270 --> 00:11:05,000
is 0.3 Hz slower than before.

161
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:06,840
Your physiological data

162
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:08,630
has fully returned to normal.

163
00:11:08,750 --> 00:11:11,960
Your muscle fibers
are 24% better than average.

164
00:11:15,150 --> 00:11:15,990
Relax.

165
00:11:16,720 --> 00:11:17,560
When I die,

166
00:11:18,270 --> 00:11:20,200
I'll lie on your table, nice and still.

167
00:11:21,840 --> 00:11:22,910
But now, you need to tell me

168
00:11:23,870 --> 00:11:25,480
if Jiang Niannian poisoned it or not.

169
00:11:28,870 --> 00:11:30,320
That bowl of medicine you sent

170
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:32,150
was different from the last one.

171
00:11:32,910 --> 00:11:35,200
The sedative content increased by 33.3%.

172
00:11:36,960 --> 00:11:38,510
As for this snowflake crisp,

173
00:11:47,150 --> 00:11:48,720
its sweetness,

174
00:11:48,720 --> 00:11:49,790
texture,

175
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:51,150
and cream ratio

176
00:11:51,150 --> 00:11:52,510
are all decent.

177
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:58,120
But if this were to take you down,

178
00:11:59,510 --> 00:12:00,910
based on your weight,

179
00:12:02,200 --> 00:12:04,270
you'd need to consume

180
00:12:04,270 --> 00:12:05,440
at least a ton of it continuously.

181
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:12,030
And what about the scented oil report?

182
00:12:15,360 --> 00:12:17,320
I'd actually advise you to use less of it.

183
00:12:18,630 --> 00:12:19,840
Why?

184
00:12:20,030 --> 00:12:21,870
The sedative components in the fragrance

185
00:12:22,390 --> 00:12:23,670
interact with your medicine.

186
00:12:24,670 --> 00:12:26,390
If your sleep improves

187
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:28,080
and you live a few more years,

188
00:12:28,840 --> 00:12:31,320
how long will I have to wait to dissect you?

189
00:12:32,630 --> 00:12:33,470
(Jiang Niannian.)

190
00:12:34,030 --> 00:12:36,270
(Are you just someone's pawn)

191
00:12:36,390 --> 00:12:37,630
(or the one playing the game?)

192
00:12:38,320 --> 00:12:40,240
(Did you ever truly love me?)

193
00:12:43,630 --> 00:12:45,480
Have you been under too much stress?

194
00:12:45,480 --> 00:12:46,910
Are you getting paranoid?

195
00:12:47,690 --> 00:12:48,550
Want me to

196
00:12:48,550 --> 00:12:50,840
give you some counseling?

197
00:12:59,240 --> 00:13:01,960
I bet you want my heart out for that.

198
00:13:08,790 --> 00:13:10,440
So you figured it out.

199
00:13:16,080 --> 00:13:17,030
Jiang Niannian.

200
00:13:18,030 --> 00:13:18,870
Niannian?

201
00:13:24,030 --> 00:13:25,000
Niannian?

202
00:13:46,030 --> 00:13:48,440
Find Jiang Niannian right now!

203
00:13:56,150 --> 00:13:57,240
It's Bloody Peony.

204
00:13:57,670 --> 00:13:59,320
She hasn't shown up for a long time.

205
00:13:59,320 --> 00:14:01,120
I heard she got married again.

206
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:03,000
I heard it's the Li family.

207
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:05,720
Who would marry a widow
who's "killed" three husbands?

208
00:14:06,320 --> 00:14:07,630
Always flaunting herself,

209
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:09,160
dreaming she'll rise to the top.

210
00:14:18,270 --> 00:14:19,110
Waiter.

211
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:36,720
This is so dull.

212
00:14:37,360 --> 00:14:38,600
The wine's

213
00:14:38,960 --> 00:14:40,120
as bad as the people here.

214
00:14:47,670 --> 00:14:48,510
What about this one?

215
00:14:52,960 --> 00:14:54,670
What a gorgeous drink.

216
00:14:55,240 --> 00:14:56,200
What's it called?

217
00:14:57,080 --> 00:14:58,200
I made it just for you.

218
00:14:59,960 --> 00:15:00,960
Because it's me.

219
00:15:05,790 --> 00:15:06,630
Jiang Niannian.

220
00:15:08,790 --> 00:15:10,320
I thought I'd never find you.

221
00:15:11,550 --> 00:15:13,120
You've got the wrong person,

222
00:15:13,120 --> 00:15:13,960
handsome.

223
00:15:21,220 --> 00:15:27,810
♪Stitched-up lips
tear open a blood-red dusk♪

224
00:15:29,620 --> 00:15:35,830
♪You return reborn,
seeing through all my cracks♪

225
00:15:36,380 --> 00:15:43,380
♪This tenderness, a trap or a gift?♪

226
00:15:44,130 --> 00:15:46,600
♪Still, I'd wager my next life on it♪

227
00:15:47,270 --> 00:15:48,110
Jiang Niannian.

228
00:15:49,480 --> 00:15:51,240
Why do you always leave me behind?

229
00:15:52,790 --> 00:15:53,630
Ye Lang.

230
00:15:54,360 --> 00:15:55,870
We were never meant to walk the same path.

231
00:15:56,340 --> 00:15:59,340
♪Lighting the edges of my frozen wings♪

232
00:15:59,360 --> 00:16:01,870
You don't know
what kind of person I really am.

233
00:16:04,110 --> 00:16:09,860
♪Breaking free
from dead vines in the ashes♪

234
00:16:11,610 --> 00:16:13,390
I... I don't need to know.

235
00:16:16,360 --> 00:16:17,550
As long as it's you, that's enough.

236
00:16:18,050 --> 00:16:22,540
♪Freeing me from this half-life prison♪

237
00:16:22,570 --> 00:16:27,400
♪As the bells shatter the past♪

238
00:16:27,800 --> 00:16:30,770
♪Life finds its way again♪

239
00:16:30,790 --> 00:16:31,750
(Ye Lang.)

240
00:16:32,000 --> 00:16:32,870
(Sorry.)

241
00:16:33,480 --> 00:16:34,910
(Before I find Xiaodi,)

242
00:16:35,480 --> 00:16:36,870
(I still need to use you)

243
00:16:36,870 --> 00:16:38,150
(to find who's behind this.)

244
00:16:40,170 --> 00:16:46,010
♪La la la♪

245
00:17:08,400 --> 00:17:14,990
♪Stitched-up lips
tear open a blood-red dusk♪

246
00:17:16,800 --> 00:17:23,010
♪You return reborn,
seeing through all my cracks♪

247
00:17:23,560 --> 00:17:30,560
♪This tenderness, a trap or a gift?♪

248
00:17:31,310 --> 00:17:33,780
♪Still, I'd wager my next life on it♪

249
00:17:33,780 --> 00:17:38,780
♪Just for a moment to recognize you again♪

250
00:17:38,780 --> 00:17:43,010
♪You are the blazing light in my despair♪

251
00:17:43,520 --> 00:17:47,450
♪Lighting the edges of my frozen wings♪

252
00:17:47,500 --> 00:17:51,290
♪I burn myself,
leaping into an illusion of fire♪

253
00:17:51,290 --> 00:17:57,040
♪Breaking free
from dead vines in the ashes♪

254
00:17:57,040 --> 00:18:01,360
♪You are the brightest star in the night♪

255
00:18:01,400 --> 00:18:05,220
♪Awakening my dormant fate♪

256
00:18:05,230 --> 00:18:09,720
♪Freeing me from this half-life prison♪

257
00:18:09,750 --> 00:18:14,580
♪As the bells shatter the past♪

258
00:18:14,980 --> 00:18:21,520
♪Life finds its way again♪

